{"id":"332470916_Sharing_More_Information_in_Visual_Cryptography_Scheme_with_Block_Expansion","abstract":"Visual cryptography scheme (VCS) shares secret image into shadows. Without computing, stacking shadows can reveal the secret image. In this paper, we propose a VCS with block expansion. Each shadow pixel is expanded into a 4-pixel block with extra secret information embedded in. In the revealing process, the secret image can be revealed by stacking shadows. In the meanwhile, we can reveal the extra shared secret information by computation.","authors":["Peng Li","Ching-Nung Yang","Dan Tang","Jianfeng Ma"],"meta":["January 2020","DOI:10.1007/978-3-030-16946-6_69","In book: Security with Intelligent Computing and Big-data Services (pp.849-857)"],"references":["305517239_A_novel_two-in-one_image_secret_sharing_scheme_based_on_perfect_black_visual_cryptography","324488153_A_construction_method_of_t_k_n_-essential_secret_image_sharing_scheme","287796931_Essential_secret_image_sharing_scheme_with_the_same_size_of_shadows","279333733_Probabilistic_Visual_Cryptography_Schemes","276159740_Reducing_shadow_size_in_essential_secret_image_sharing_by_conjunctive_hierarchical_approach","272392530_Non-expansible_XOR-based_visual_cryptography_scheme_with_meaningful_shares","265388848_Extended_Capabilities_for_XOR-Based_Visual_Cryptography","262243369_Essential_secret_image_sharing_scheme_with_different_importance_of_shadows","260519186_Property_Analysis_of_XOR-Based_Visual_Cryptography","259141849_Sharing_more_information_in_gray_visual_cryptography_scheme","238909988_Constructions_and_properties_of_k_out_of_n_scalable_secret_image_sharing","224221671_Embedded_Extended_Visual_Cryptography_Schemes","223523250_On_general_construction_for_extended_visual_cryptography_schemes","222839888_Secret_image_sharing","222650484_New_visual_secret_sharing_schemes_using_probabilistic_method","222412690_Visual_secret_sharing_for_multiple_secrets","222164068_VCPSS_A_two-in-one_two-decoding-option